### 角色管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 创建角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roleName": "测试角色",
  "roleCode": "test_role",
  "description": "这是一个测试角色",
  "status": 1
}

### 更新角色
PUT {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roleName": "更新后的角色名",
  "description": "更新后的描述",
  "status": 1
}

### 删除角色
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据ID查询角色
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 分页查询角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/page
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "current": 1,
  "size": 10,
  "keyword": "",
  "status": null
}

### 获取所有角色列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 分配角色权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/1/assign-permission
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menuIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
}

### 获取角色已分配的菜单ID列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/role/1/menu-ids
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

